    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036520/extras/SteamAbout.PNG?t=1749542287\" /></span><br>Rome (the penguin) Goes Rogue is a sandbox-y physics based take on the roguelite genre with emphasis on chaining combos and attacks taking place in a submarine with randomly generated chaos.  Use abilities, props, hazards and your flippers to stop the robots and escape the submarine.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036520/extras/SteamFeatures.PNG?t=1749542287\" /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A Submarine with randomly pick floors, enemies, hazards and props<br></li><li> Random enemy and prop placement, stats, and behaviors<br></li><li> 25+ Upgrades and abilities<br></li><li> 20 Mutators that can vary the game<br></li><li> Custom Game mode, where you can edit almost every stat in the game<br></li><li> Physics based combat system<br></li><li> Unique randomized hazards that spawn on every floor<br></li><li> Built in level editor<br></li><li> Available for Mac &amp; Linux<br></li><li> Penguins<br></li><li> Be able to kill enemies with anything<br></li><li> And random goals through out each floor!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036520/extras/Conditions.GIF?t=1749542287\" /></span></li></ul>",
